                    <span>I question the security background of any of those who read this book and gave it a good review. The author's approach security leaves huge gaps and what is covered is written in a simplistic form... probably because the author only understands a small amount of the topic she is writing about.<P>I question the author's own ability to secure an environment, and she should probably not be teaching others.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Information Security Architechture by Jan Tudor</div>
