                    <span>I am a CSS student with the College of North Atlantic, St.John's <BR>, Newfoundland. I think that Jan Tudor has put together the "manual" for security within the buisness structure. I am amazed at the debt and scope of this book as there is no stone unturned and information technology people would be at a loss not to read and understand just how security or the lack of it can make or break a buisness, large or small.A true work of art, thanks Jan.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">THOROUGH REFERENCE GUIDE</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
